---

This project is based on SDL2 Raycasting Engine by Andrew Lim:
https://github.com/andrew-lim/sdl2-raycast

The BennuGD2 port includes significant modifications and extensions:
- Integration with BennuGD2 game engine
- Multi-level system (3 independent levels)
- Enhanced door animation system
- Billboard sprite system with multiple directions
- Configurable fog system
- Real-time minimap
- Spawn flag system
- Qt-based map editor
- Custom .raymap file format
